dct_description_sm: Map includes legend of roads and transport; monuments and culture; topography and hydrography; tourism and hiking. Verso provides written descriptions (in parallel Modern Greek and English) and photographs of the island's terrain; history and monuments; scenic touring and hiking routes. Includes list of telephone numbers useful to hikers and tourists. Verso provides four detail maps of hiking routes.
